      modeling_assumptions:
        chiplet_type_mapping: All original ChipletPart blocks are represented as synthetic
          3dblox dies.
        chiplet_shape_mapping: Each block is converted into a square die with side
          sqrt(area_mm2) * 1000 microns.
        region_mapping: Each die uses one synthetic front-side region named core_reg.
        stack_mapping: All dies are placed on a 2D shelf grid at z = 0 with orient
          = R0.
        connection_mapping: No native 3dblox Connection section is emitted because
          the source testcase does not provide region-to-region physical connectivity.
        collateral_mapping: No standard external collateral keys are populated because
          the source testcase does not include LEF/liberty/tech/deck collateral.
